130
00:06:01.327 --> 00:06:02.829
That's probably true.

131
00:06:02.871 --> 00:06:05.123
but I drove all the way out
to bumfuck Connecticut. so...

132
00:06:05.165 --> 00:06:06.332
Where'd you come from?

133
00:06:06.833 --> 00:06:07.792
You mean. where do I live?

134
00:06:08.376 --> 00:06:09.252
Sure.

135
00:06:12.213 --> 00:06:13.173
Murray Hill.

136
00:06:13.923 --> 00:06:14.841
I'm in Chelsea.

137
00:06:15.175 --> 00:06:16.843
(SIGHS) Yeah. cool.

138
00:06:17.093 --> 00:06:18.928
