boyfriend named Derek.

152
00:06:46.206 --> 00:06:49.209
And I didn't have to fuck
Alex Le Domas to get it.

153
00:06:49.250 --> 00:06:50.376
I did it all by myself.

154
00:06:52.253 --> 00:06:53.880
