187
00:08:37.525 --> 00:08:39.193
So they hunted me.

188
00:08:40.945 --> 00:08:46.576
I got shot through the hand.
beat to shit by a butler.

189
00:08:49.704 --> 00:08:50.747
And my...

190
00:08:53.416 --> 00:08:55.460
My husband stabbed me.

191
