195
00:09:12.143 --> 00:09:12.935
No.

196
00:09:15.480 --> 00:09:16.522
They blew up.

197
00:09:18.358 --> 00:09:19.609
They blew up?

198
00:09:20.526 --> 00:09:23.529
And then after they blew up.
there was a guy in a chair.

199
00:09:25.490 --> 00:09:27.367
And he nodded at me.

200
00:09:28.951 --> 00:09:32.080
Who was the guy in the chair?

201
00:09:33.206 --> 00:09:34.248
I don't know.

202
00:09:36.000 --> 00:09:38.378
But he was see-through
so I'm pretty sure he was...

203
00:09:39.670 --> 00:09:40.797
...you know.

204
00:09:47.345 --> 00:09:48.721
(INHALES)

205
00:09:48.763 --> 00:09:50.348
You are so going to jail.

206
