Ven acá. tía.

241
00:12:15.826 --> 00:12:17.245
Ay. Dios.

242
00:12:17.286 --> 00:12:19.080
All right. t-tell William
to gas up the jet.

243
00:12:19.121 --> 00:12:22.542
